     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts mappingEvenementCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"mappingEvenementCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"hcmappingEvenementCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Groupe 1 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-evenement</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-documentation-of</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEvenement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>documentationOf</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEvenement.identifiantEvenement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.id</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEvenement.codeEvenement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEvenement.dateHeureEvenement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.effectiveTime</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEvenement.executantEvenement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.performer@typeCode=\"PRF\"</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEvenement.executantEvenement.roleFonctionnel</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.performer.functionCode</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEvenement.executantEvenement.dateHeureParticipation</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.performer.time</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMEvenement.executantEvenement.executant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.performer.assignedEntity</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Groupe 2 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-documentation-of</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-composition-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td><td><b>Commentaire</b></td></tr><tr><td>documentationOf</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.event</td><td/></tr><tr><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.id</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #efefef\">(not mapped)</td><td style=\"background-color: #efefef\">Cette donnée est fournie dans un autre élément : Composition.relatesTo</td></tr><tr><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.event.code</td><td/></tr><tr><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.effectiveTime</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.event.period</td><td/></tr><tr><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.performer@typeCode=\"PRF\"</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.event.extension:perfomer.PractitionerRole</td><td>Composition.event.extension:perfomer.ValueReference.resolve().ofType(FrPractitionerRoleDocument)</td></tr><tr><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.performer.functionCode</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.event.extension:perfomer.PractitionerRole.code</td><td/></tr><tr><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.performer.time</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #efefef\">(not mapped)</td><td style=\"background-color: #efefef\">Mapped in Composition.event.period </td></tr><tr><td>documentationOf.serviceEvent.performer.assignedEntity</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>Composition.event.extension:perfomer.PractitionerRole.Practitioner</td><td>Composition.event.extension:perfomer.ValueReference.resolve().ofType(FrPractitionerRoleDocument).Practitioner.resolve()</td></tr></table></div>"
